Stop, the 3 lights then I think went around each other, ?? Anticlocwise, Then Above us flying out to sea, hovering , back and forth.. Hmm Now that sort of manouvering (sorry spelling problems) surley would have liquified a Human occupant ??, let alone the stucture, and close proximity of each other ??
